Event(s):	JenExp_2010 (Jena Experiment 2010) * LATITUDE: 50.946100 * LONGITUDE: 11.611300 * DATE/TIME START: 2010-01-01T00:00:00 * DATE/TIME END: 2010-12-31T00:00:00 * LOCATION: Thuringia, Germany * METHOD/DEVICE: Experiment (EXP)
Parameter(s):	Experimental plot (Experimental plot) * COMMENT: Detailed explanations of plots and the plant diversity gradient are provided in the section "further details".
